    "rich_text_VE4tgd": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "title_q7ErAj": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Building a National Community of Care",
            "title_size": "h3",
            "seo_h_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_QURTzt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With our retail stores in locations across the country, including Athlone, Galway, Ballyhaunis, Castlebar, Ennis, Dundalk, Limerick, Tralee, Dublin and Waterford we are building a national community servicing the needs of carers, the cared-for and self-carers.<\/p>",
            "text_size": "large"
          }
        },
        "text_wByN7U": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our expert in-store staff are ready to help you find the best product or service for you, whether you’re modifying your home or simply making everyday changes.<\/p>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
