    "91317d70-2c8d-47c1-a95f-a74f7d6d49c9": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "template--20685976404315__91317d70-2c8d-47c1-a95f-a74f7d6d49c9-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>With our in-depth knowledge we have developed a suite of services that wrap around our products, ensuring you or your loved one can stay in their home as long as possible. <\/li><li>Our nationwide network of stores means we’re available where you are. Over the past three decades we’ve built a national community servicing the needs of carers, the cared-for and self-carers. Our in-store staff are empathetic and knowledgeable, and they are expertly placed to help you find the products and services you need.<\/li><li>If you’d like to find out more about how we can help you contact your nearest store today to speak with a Customer Care Representative, who will be happy to assist you with your essential care, health and wellness needs.<br\/><\/li><\/ul>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
